3. Automatic Authentication Detection 🔐

Your tool should automatically detect login mechanisms.

Look for:

Login Forms

Fields like:

username
email
password
login
API Login

Look for:

POST /api/login
POST /auth/login
POST /api/token
Token Authentication

Detect headers like:

Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
JWT Detection

Check if token format is:

xxxxx.yyyyy.zzzzz
